<subSubSection pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="39.[151,1436,151,573]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,295,320]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[674,863,296,320]" class="Insecta" family="Yponomeutidae" genus="Argyresthia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curvativa" subGenus="Argyresthia">
<emphasis box="[674,699,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">A.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[716,740,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">A.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[757,863,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">curvativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the male genitalia. It can be separated from the latter by the forewing having a longitudinal dark grayish-fuscous streak extending from the costal 2/5 to 2/3 and a dark grayish fuscous dorsal fascia from before the middle of the wing extending nearly to the longitudinal costal streak, and in the male genitalia by the saccus 1.6 times as long as the width of the valva. 
<taxonomicName box="[1144,1436,404,428]" class="Insecta" family="Yponomeutidae" genus="Argyresthia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curvativa" subGenus="Argyresthia">
<emphasis box="[1144,1275,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Argyresthia</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1290,1315,404,427]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">A.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1330,1436,405,428]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">curvativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
lacks a longitudinal streak along the costa and has a blackish gray dorsal fascia extending from the middle of the wing to above the upper angle of the cell, and the saccus is shorter than the width of the valva in the male genitalia.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="39.[151,1436,151,573]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,511,536]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Etymology.</emphasis>
